Description: Forced reset platform theme
 The app crashes if Gtk2 platform theme is in use. This patch avoids
 conflicts with built-in GTK integration.
Author: Nicholas Guriev <guriev-ns@ya.ru>
Last-Updated: Sun, 09 Feb 2020 20:40:07 +0300
--- a/Telegram/SourceFiles/platform/linux/specific_linux.cpp
+++ b/Telegram/SourceFiles/platform/linux/specific_linux.cpp
@@ -249,6 +249,7 @@ int psFixPrevious() {
 namespace Platform {
 
 void start() {
+	unsetenv("QT_QPA_PLATFORMTHEME");
 	FallbackFontConfig();
 }
 
